	   <tr><td colspan=2>Don't forget Bards, charisma is just as important to them as it is to enchanters.&nbsp;&nbsp;If not more so...  Why is it more important u ask?..Well lets just say the bard is being used for crowd control.. With the bards mez only lasting 15seconds, he must have as little resisted mezzes as possible, if 2 gets resisted in the 15 second cycle, the bard is going to get behind in it (figuring he is keeping 4 mezzed).  Hence it is crucial for the bard not to get resisted, an enchanter has much more opportunity (ie. time) to re-mez..<br><br>Wiever<br>54 Bard <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
